  content: `# ${companyName} - Business Operating System\n\n> Systematic business organization powered by AI-driven entropy management\n\n## ğŸ¯ Overview\n\nThis repository contains the complete Business Operating System (B-OS) for ${companyName}, organized using the systematic 0-9 framework for maximum clarity and zero organizational overhead.\n\n## ğŸ—ï¸ Structure\n\n${domains.map(domain => `### ${domain.number}. ${domain.name}\nğŸ“ [\`${domain.number.toString().padStart(2, '0')}-${domain.name.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]/g, '-')}/\`](./${domain.number.toString().padStart(2, '0')}-${domain.name.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]/g, '-')}/)\n${domain.content?.[0] || 'Business domain for ' + domain.name}\n`).join('\n')}
